Author: 01BTC
Title: [ANN] [PRE-SALE] AcuteCoin.io | POW | POS | Masternodes - Trade, Mine be Social
Body: About the AcuteCoin Platform  The AcuteCoin platform provides users with multiple opportunities and an exclusive crypto community that both learn and earn by sharing and building their crypto portfolios together. AcuteCoin strives to be both a platform for earning and a useful tool in helping you maneuver your way through this exciting industry. AcuteCoin itself will be the utility coin for use on the platform, for users to earn revenue through a select group of services that we have established from the ground up with our partners.  While AcuteCoin is a Lending platform its main focus will be on a sustainable platform based on revenues outside of lending which will maintain the platform for all Users.  While other Lending platforms have failed to sustain itself AcuteCoin will create longevity through its multiple income streams outside of Lending.  This is the main goal of the AcuteCoin project and its focus.  Other Lending platforms are solely based on new subscribers and creating income from trading bots which don’t always work.  We have seen how lending platforms start off strong but slowly wither away.  AcuteCoin isn’t just a Lending platform as it will focus on other sustainable revenue streams.  AcuteCoin will focus on the actual trading of coins across various markets and constructing a physical mining operation located in an economically friendly environment and be able to provide users with mining contracts.  ICO Funds will also be used to build out a social platform where Users and AcuteCoin traders can make trades together and earn together.  Our "lending" mechanism on the platform is simply a Proof of Stake reward system where Users are rewarded for helping to stabilize the coin circulation and network.  Community members will be invited to take on specific roles on the platform to help improve community involvement and provide more transparency.  We are acting on past mistakes by other platforms and the need for a community based investment alternative to help improve the image of crypto. As well there is an obvious demand for this sort of platform for newer entries into the cryptocurrency space. The AcuteCoin platform seeks to be a platform that respects those in crypto that work to expand its adoption and shed a positive image on the space overall.   The AcuteCoin platform will be supported by an ICO of 10,000,000 total coins that will begin on July 1, 2018 with a pre-ICO sale beginning on May 1, 2018.  Prior to our ICO launch, there will be an Airdrop of 100K AcuteCoin starting on April 4, 2018 where users that signup to our platform will receive FREE coins. AcuteCoin will also offer a bounty program and distribute 10,000 total AcuteCoin coins to be shared amongst our affiliate partners.  The bounty will go hand in hand with our Affiliate program which is a further incentive for all Users to benefit from.  A platform which provides the subscriber the opportunity to earn AcuteCoin generated via 3 main avenues in crypto currency, its hard coded proof of stake mechanism, external physical mining of crypto currencies and the building of a solid portfolio of crypto assets while supporting proven projects in the space.  We welcome all new participants and look forward to you being a part of this new and exciting project.
